Create (or fetch existing) draft of an org-level lens. Idempotent — same user calling twice returns the same draft. The returned lens has `draft_of` set to the original lens id.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} when a non-admin needs to modify an org-level lens — make a draft, edit the draft.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} from agent flow — leadbay_adjust_audience handles the draft-routing transparently.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
